WEBVTT

38:22.020 --> 38:24.920 line:80%
with those looks,
not only is Song Yan far behind,

38:25.020 --> 38:26.360 line:80%
in our entire Lin'an Town—

38:26.360 --> 38:28.280 line:80%
no, in the whole Qingping County—
you can't find another.

38:27.480 --> 38:32.010 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

38:28.310 --> 38:29.030 line:80%
Exactly.
